sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy)
    participant KubeAuth as kube-auth-proxy
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant ModelCtrl as odh-model-controller
    participant Runtime as vLLM / TGIS / MLServer
    participant S3 as S3 Storage
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 1: Model Deployment via Dashboard

    User->>Gateway: Login via HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KubeAuth: ext_authz (EnvoyFilter)
    KubeAuth->>KubeAuth: OAuth2/OIDC authentication<br/>+ SubjectAccessReview
    KubeAuth-->>Gateway: Authenticated
    Gateway-->>Dashboard: HTTPRoute to Dashboard
    Dashboard-->>User: Show model serving UI

    User->>Dashboard: Select model, runtime,<br/>hardware profile
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>(SA token, HTTPS/443)
    K8sAPI-->>KServe: Watch event: new InferenceService

    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + Service<br/>+ storage init container
    KServe->>S3: Init container downloads<br/>model artifacts (HTTPS/443)
    KServe->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService status

    ModelCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch: InferenceService ready
    ModelCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>(referencing shared Gateway)
    ModelCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)
    ModelCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor

    Runtime->>Runtime: Load model weights,<br/>warm up inference engine

    Note over Client,Runtime: Production Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/my-model:predict<br/>(HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+)
    Gateway->>KubeAuth: ext_authz authentication
    KubeAuth-->>Gateway: Authorized
    Gateway->>Runtime: HTTPRoute to runtime pod<br/>(mTLS via Istio)
    Runtime->>Runtime: Execute inference
    Runtime-->>Gateway: Prediction response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response (HTTPS)

    User->>Dashboard: View model metrics + status
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Query InferenceService status
    Dashboard->>ModelReg: Get model metadata<br/>(gRPC/9090)
    Dashboard-->>User: Show serving dashboard
